<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="mn">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CHADWAR</title>

    <!-- Google Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: #f5f6fa;
            color: #111;
        }
        
        .container {
            width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        /* NAVBAR */
        
        header {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #5B3DF5;
        }
        
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .auth {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: #5B3DF5;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        /* HERO */
        
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        
        .hero-text {
            width: 50%;
        }
        
        .badge {
            background: #e6e9ff;
            color: #5B3DF5;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            color: #5B3DF5;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .search-box {
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .search-box input {
            padding: 12px;
            width: 300px;
            border-radius: 25px 0 0 25px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            outline: none;
        }
        
        .search-box button {
            border-radius: 0 25px 25px 0;
        }
        
        .hero img {
            width: 500px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        /* CATEGORIES */
        
        .section {
            padding: 60px 0;
        }
        
        .section h2 {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .categories {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .category-card {
            flex: 1;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        
        .category-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        /* SERVICES */
        
        .services {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .service-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 25%;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .service-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        
        .service-content {
            padding: 15px;
        }
        
        .price {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #5B3DF5;
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container navbar">
            <div class="logo">⚡ CHADWAR</div>

            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="#">Нүүр хуудас</a>
                <a href="#">Үйлчилгээ</a>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='freelancers.html'">
                    Чөлөөт ажилтнууд
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="auth">
                <a href="#">Нэвтрэх</a>
                <button class="btn-primary">Бүртгүүлэх</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero container">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <div class="badge">Монголын №1 Фрийланс Платформ</div>

            <h1>
                Таны төсөлд тохирох <br>
                <span class="highlight">Мэргэжлийн Ажилтан</span>
            </h1>

            <p>
                Бизнесийн хэрэгцээнд нийцсэн шилдэг чөлөөт ажилтнуудыг холбож өгнө.
            </p>

            <div class="search-box">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Ямар үйлчилгээ хайж байна вэ?">
                <button class="btn-primary">Хайх</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521737604893-d14cc237f11d" alt="Team working">
    </section>

    <section class="section container">
        <h2>Үйлчилгээний ангилал</h2>

        <div class="categories">
            <div class="category-card">График Дизайн</div>
            <div class="category-card">Програмчлал</div>
            <div class="category-card">Маркетинг</div>
            <div class="category-card">Орчуулга</div>
            <div class="category-card">Видео & Анимэйшн</div>
            <div class="category-card">Дуу & Аудио</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section container">
        <h2>Эрэлттэй үйлчилгээ</h2>

        <div class="services">
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492724441997-5dc865305da7">
                <div class="service-content">
                    <h4>Вэб дизайн үйлчилгээ</h4>
                    <p>4.9 ⭐ (128)</p>
                    <div class="price">₮250,000</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559027615-cd4628902d4a">
                <div class="service-content">
                    <h4>Брэнд лого дизайн</h4>
                    <p>5.0 ⭐ (342)</p>
                    <div class="price">₮150,000</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f">
                <div class="service-content">
                    <h4>Сошиал маркетинг</h4>
                    <p>4.8 ⭐ (24)</p>
                    <div class="price">₮80,000</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085">
                <div class="service-content">
                    <h4>Орчуулгын үйлчилгээ</h4>
                    <p>4.9 ⭐ (89)</p>
                    <div class="price">₮30,000</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        © 2026 CHADWAR. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

</body>

</html>
